args: Yo, this castle is HUGE!\nStrongest-lookin' I've ever seen!
But we're still stronger. Come on, Chariot,\nlet's show 'em what's what!
The hell? Is he tryin' to fight the\ncastle itself?
It seems less like fighting and more like...\nriding around in circles.
This castle won't know which way is up\nonce I'M through with it!
We got a weirdo on our hands, boss.
Let's just hear what he has to say.
Excuse me, can we talk for a
Shove off, ya turkey! I ain't slowin' down\nfor no one!
Can't speak to his brains, but he sure ain't\nshort'a energy. Kid's like a damn tornado!
What the?! He stopped me dead!
We got some questions fer ya, kiddo.
Holy cow... You're MASSIVE! I didn't\nknow muscles could GET that big!
You gotta be the king of this castle. Right?
Bwaaa ha ha! Sorry kid, ya got the wrong\nguy. The boss is {player_name}\nover there.
THAT pipsqueak? Please. Nobody's takin'\norders from him!
Come on, a castle this big's gotta have\na real giant of a leader!
Heh. You're not the first to tell me I\ndon't look the part of royalty.
You really came here without\nknowin' about {player_name}?\nThere's rare for ya.
Well yeah. I saw this castle from a ways\noff, so I just hopped on my chariot and\nrolled on over.
My chariot, man! We ride together, always.\nCheck out all the spikes and junkpretty\nkeen, huh?
I'm tellin' ya, when me and my guy here\nlink up, there's no stoppin' us!
Whaddya think, boss? Should we drive\nhim off?
No, he doesn't seem to be an enemy.
Let's just leave him be for now.\nHe'll tire himself out eventually.
All right, but I ain't carrying him to bed...
Time for some night ridin'.\nGotta love that evening air!
...Kinda seems like he's just gettin'\nMORE energy.
Yeah. It's actually kind of impressive.
{player_name}, would you please\ndo something about that racket?
Guess seein' ol' Mids stopped him in\nhis tracks.
If he's interested in dragons, we may have\njust found our solution.
Midgardsormr, would you mind talking to\nhim for a while?
Hold up, this cat orders dragons around?!
Very well. I happen to have a few words\nin mind already.
Thanks. Don't be too hard on him.
I can't believe what I'm seein' right now.
This guy leads dragons. Frickin' DRAGONS!
He might not have big muscles,\nbut he's definitely king material.
Hey, sorry about callin' you pipsqueak\nbefore, Slick. I was way off base.
Yeah! That's what I'm callin' you from\nnow on, Slick. Now tell me how you\nwhipped that dragon into shape!
W-well, I did defeat him to form our pact,\nbut that's
Ha ha, hell yeah you did! Clocked\nhim clean in the kisser, I bet.
That's the kinda strength I'm after!\nYou GOTTA tell me how you do it.
Um... I guess I just train hard each day.\nOh, and I always eat my vegetables.
All right, that clinches it.\nLemme join your gang!
Er, you're welcome to join our cause,\nbut I don't think we're a gang in the\nway you're thinking.
Whatever you say, Slick! I'm yours to\ncommand from here on out.
Why do I get the feeling he has no idea\nwhat we do here?
Oh, no doubt there. Still, it sounds like\nhe's gonna heed yer beck and call,\nso at least we can keep him on a leash.
Problem solved, if ya ask me.
I will not abide anyone thinking you\nwhipped me into shape.
You will set him straight.\nAre we clear, {player_name}?
Yo, he's givin' you lip, Slick!\nWant me to whack him?
Bwa ha ha! Yer just rarin' to go, huh?
Looks like ya got yer work cut out for\nya, boss.
